== Pacification ==
* Defending the option of producers and consumers of [[#Definitions|intangibles]] to avoid double taxation by states.
** default: no double taxation
** option out (i.e., pay taxes on bits to states as well)
* Ensuring that our tax is free from cartels, cf. [http://www.zotero.org/mazsa/items/124672418 Barnett,2006]:
<blockquote>1. Focus prosecutors on “hard core” cartel activity</blockquote>

<blockquote>2. Treat cartels as serious crimes, and cartel members as criminals</blockquote>

<blockquote>3. Provide amnesty and amnesty plus</blockquote>

<blockquote>4. Vigorously prosecute obstruction of justice</blockquote>

<blockquote>5. Charge cartels in conjunction with other offenses</blockquote>

<blockquote>6. Provide transparency</blockquote>

<blockquote>7. Publicize enforcement efforts</blockquote>
